    <h2>Find quality vehicles at Chicago luxury car dealers</h2>
<p>If you&rsquo;re looking for well-appointed, expertly maintained, <a title="Used luxury cars in Chicago" href="/browse-all-luxury-cars.aspx"><strong>used luxury cars</strong></a>, Patrick's pre-owned luxury vehicles offer a unique combination of elegance and value. At Patrick, we take great pride in the extensive variety and volume of our distinctive used luxury car inventory. We can procure any model of used luxury vehicle, from luxury SUVs to luxury cars, and make you fall in love with the <a title="Pre-Owned luxury cars in Chicago" href="/browse-certified-pre-owned-cars.aspx"><strong>pre-owned luxury vehicles</strong></a> of your dreams&mdash; on your terms.</p>
<p>The staff at our <strong>used luxury car dealers in Chicago</strong> will impress you with the depth of their knowledge and their passion for customer service. There isn&rsquo;t a luxury car that the Patrick experts don&rsquo;t know inside and out. Everyone, from our friendly sales staff to our Master Technicians, are dedicated to pairing you with the<strong> pre-owned luxury vehicles</strong> you want, from <strong>luxury SUVs</strong>, to <strong>luxury sedans</strong>, to <strong>luxury cars</strong>, or any other pre-owned luxury car of your dreams.</p>
<p>Many <a title="Learn about Chicago luxury car dealers" href="/about-us.aspx"><strong>used luxury car dealers</strong></a> are relatively new to the automotive industry. Patrick isn&rsquo;t one of them. Founded in 1907 as America&rsquo;s first franchise seeded by Henry Ford, Patrick is in a league of its own. Spanning four generations of family ownership, Patrick represents a &lsquo;values-first&rsquo; commitment to quality, service, and luxury you won&rsquo;t find at other car dealers in Chicago &mdash; or anywhere else.</p>
<h2>Pre-Owned Luxury Vehicles at this Chicago Used Luxury Car Dealer</h2>
<p>When it comes to selling and servicing the finest luxury cars, our selection of <strong>used luxury cars</strong>&mdash;from Porsche to Jaguar to Ferrari&mdash;is simply unmatched. Paired with our award-winning <strong><a title="Luxury car repair in Chicago" href="/luxury-car-service.aspx">luxury car repair</a></strong> and decades of experience, shopping with Patrick is its own experience.</p>
<p>Everything about this <a title="Visit used luxury car dealers in Illinois" href="/directions-and-hours.aspx"><strong>used luxury car dealer</strong></a>&nbsp;is geared toward making you feel comfortable, informed, and satisfied with every purchase you make. The experts at Patrick know that there is simply no substitution for 5-star customer service and exceptional <strong>used luxury cars</strong>. That&rsquo;s <strong>&ldquo;The Patrick Difference&rdquo;</strong>.</p>
<p>Browse from a wide selection of well-appointed, <a title="Pre-owned luxury vehicles at the Patrick Luxury Outlet" href="/browse-certified-pre-owned-cars.aspx"><strong>pre-owned luxury vehicles</strong></a> and <a title="Used luxury cars in Chicago" href="/browse-all-luxury-cars.aspx"><strong>used luxury cars</strong></a>. <a title="Contact our Chicago luxury car dealers today" href="/contact-us.aspx">Click to contact us</a> at <strong>888-348-5006</strong> to find a specific <strong>pre-owned luxury vehicle</strong>.
